   MESSAGE IN A BOTTLE, by Nicholas Sparks. (Warner, $20.) ...... 8
.. 8 .. 14
</P>
<P>
   After finding a seaborne bottle containing an
</P>
<P>
   engimatic letter, a divorced woman enounters love.
</P>
