<P>
   A psychotic killer, returning to his Texas hometown to
</P>
<P>
   wreak vengeance, uses a troubled widow as his pawn.
</P>
<P>
   THE ELEVENTH COMMANDMENT, by Jeffrey Archer. ................ 10
.. 13 .. 4
</P>
<P>
   (HarperCollins, $26.) A veteran CIA officer must
</P>
<P>
   contend with a new enemy, the director of central intelligence.
</P>
<P>
   THE LAST FULL MEASURE, by Jeff Shaara. (Ballantine, ........ 11
.. 12 .. 6
