<P>
   THE STREET LAWYER, by John Grisham. (Doubleday, $27.95.) .... 13
.. 9 .. 23
</P>
<P>
   A young lawyer comes to terms with himself after discovering his
</P>
<P>
   prestigious firm's dirty secret.
</P>
<P>
   MEMOIRS OF A GEISHA, by Arthur Golden. (Knopf, $25.) ...... 14
.. 10 .. 35
