<P>
   PIZZA-DELIVERERS _ Depending on how you slice it, pizza delivery
drivers pay a high price for the privilege of delivering those
pepperoni pies. Many young drivers hop in the their cars not
thinking who would foot the bill should they cause an accident
while on a run. (Drummond, Dayton Daily News)
