Presbyterian.'' And proving that sometimes the apple does fall far
from the tree,  &UR; Judy Wolf  &LR; was eating in a Sacramento cafe when she
saw a father wearing a T-shirt that said ``Jesus'' accompanied by
his son wearing a T-shirt that said ``Godzilla.''
</P>
