<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-19 20:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2367 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GYM-GOODWILL-GAMES-NY     07-19 0610
