<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-19 22:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2423 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEACH-TEST-775(2TAKES     07-19 0819
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEACH-TEST-775(2TAKES)-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TEACHERS UNION PURSUING QUALITY CONTROL
</HEADLINE>
   (jw) 
 By ETHAN BRONNER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW ORLEANS _ John Cole, president of the Texas Federation of
Teachers, objects to what he says has been the most widely used
